    {
      "id": "626627791b0749001d51f241",
      "text": "シーニュ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1650861948,
      "updated": 1650861948
    },
    {
      "id": "626627bfb8bbfc00005387ac",
      "text": "[signe]の日本語読み",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1650862016,
      "updated": 1650868565
    },
    {
      "id": "6266277db8bbfc00005387aa",
      "text": "[シニフィアン]と[シニフィエ]の対",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1650861950,
      "updated": 1721472446
    },
    {
      "id": "669b95ab5b98c20000d04309",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1721472428,
      "updated": 1721472428
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e7c500000000004bd62e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592261,
      "updated": 1777592261
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c94",
      "text": "from [signe]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c95",
      "text": "シーニュ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c96",
      "text": "[signifiant]と[signifié]の[恣意的]な結びつきのこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c97",
      "text": " 日本語読みだと[シーニュ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c98",
      "text": " フランス語で[signe]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c99",
      "text": " [ソシュール]の定義による",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9a",
      "text": "　どういうことか具体的でわかりやすい例が[wiki https://www.wikiwand.com/ja/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A7%E3%83%AB%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E3%83%8A%E3%83%B3%E3%83%BB%E3%83%89%E3%83%BB%E3%82%BD%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB#/%E4%BA%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%88%86%E7%AF%80]に載っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9b",
      "text": "　[シニフィアンとシニフィエ - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%B7%E3%83%8B%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%82%A2%E3%83%B3%E3%81%A8%E3%82%B7%E3%83%8B%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%82%A8]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9d",
      "text": "[https://kotobank.jp/word/意味-32260 意味(いみ)とは？ 意味や使い方 - コトバンク]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9e",
      "text": " 日本大百科全書(ニッポニカ)の項が [signifiant] と [signifié] の関係に近いことが書いてあると思う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867c9f",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/9f48d28bfb033c01f3777e02ced6ae92]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca0",
      "text": "  この図の[\" [記号]] が[signifiant]、[\" [意味]]が [signifié]、[\" [指示物]]が [référent]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca1",
      "text": "   実際のものを使った図は描けなさそう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca2",
      "text": "    例: 木を表す場合",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca3",
      "text": "     [référent] として実写の画像[木(実写).icon]を使い、[signifiant] とし記号て🌳を使ったとして、[signifié] の表現ができない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca4",
      "text": "      「木」は[signifiant]として解釈できるため",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca5",
      "text": " 図がエライことになってる🤣",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca6",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/499ffa4789c82bc8bd0efc57a8dc949a]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca8",
      "text": "[/komoji-od/蝶も蛾もパピヨンみたいなやつ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867ca9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867caa",
      "text": "素人が書いているので、かなり間違っているかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cab",
      "text": " 専門の人もしいたら直しておいて下さい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cad",
      "text": "20世紀に[- 発見]発明された[概念]としては最重要リストに絶対はいると思っている[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cae",
      "text": " 革命興すレベルの超重要概念[takker.icon*3]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867caf",
      "text": " 一度触れると、この概念が「ない」状態を考えられなくなる。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cb0",
      "text": " \tそのくらい強い。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cb2",
      "text": "言語によって文化が生まれることに繋がってそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cb3",
      "text": "\t逆に言語を習得するには表面上の意味や文法だけじゃなくて[文化]をしる必要がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e6ce0000000000867cb4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592014,
      "updated": 1777592014
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e7ba00000000004bd62d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592249,
      "updated": 1777592249
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb0",
      "text": "from [シニフィアンとシニフィエ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592204
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb2",
      "text": "table:比較",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb3",
      "text": "　[シニフィアン]\t[signifiant]\t[能記]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb4",
      "text": "　[シニフィエ]\t[signifié]\t[所記]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592204
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb6",
      "text": "code: s.mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb7",
      "text": "  graph 　TD",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb8",
      "text": "  A[シニフィアン（音声表現）] --> B[シニフィエ（心理的な意味内容）]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bb9",
      "text": "  B --> A",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592204
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bbb",
      "text": " [シーニュ]（[signe]）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592240
    },
    {
      "id": "69f3e78c00000000003f4bbc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777592204,
      "updated": 1777592204
    },
    {
